				<h2>Description</h2>
				<p class="desc-pa"> The best thing in the world is when we make something with our own hands. Creating smoothies not only benefits us with a healthy lifestyle, but a way for us to connect with nature. A smoothie at its core is made of fruits. Creating a smoothie is the same as painting an art. In order for us to deliver this experience to everyone, we introduce an outright environment of smoothies. We provide a thorough explanation of our recipes that encourage everyone a chance to try this at home. In this way, people can understand more about smoothie from A to Z. Besides, we let them know our tips and tricks for creating the best smoothies ever. Everyone has a different taste; that is why our recipes will guide them to alter their smoothies based on their own preferences. Not only that, but we also promote the benefits of consuming smoothies in our daily lives. To make it easy for everyone to follow, we divide our sections into 4 categories, Ingredients, videos, tips &amp; tricks and ‘Did you know?’. Ingredients are for those who prefer no guidance but only through reading. On the other hands, videos will help those who prefer guidance and detailed explanation. Tips &amp; tricks allow people to alter their own smoothies. Lastly, ‘Did you know?’ is for giving insight about smoothies benefits. </p>
